  <description><![CDATA[<p>This welcoming family-run hotel is located near the colourful marina area of Riva, just 100 metres from the lakeside and beach, a further 15 minute lakeside stroll to the historical resort centre. With plenty to interest close at hand, the hotel's verdant garden and attractive poolside offer the ideal relaxing retreat. Guests at the Brione will appreciate the hospitality of the Modena family and the great services and facilities they provide.</p>]]></description>
